    ApcUps - Plasma widget and data engine to monitor the status of
             APC-brand Uninterruptible Power Supplies.

Overview

    A KDE Plasma component that monitors uninterruptible power
    supplies controlled by apcupsd <http://www.apcupsd.com/>.
    It can connect to any UPS (or more precisely: any apcupsd
    daemon) which is reachable over the network.
    
Installation

    See the INSTALL file for details on how to build and install the software.
    Alternatively, packages are available for certain distros. Check the web
    site for details.
    
